strings: <voice_0x01000FE8><se_def>*: And I have the mirror of King Argonaut!
<voice_0x01000FE9><se_def>*: I don't know where I took this. But in the end I was able to fight Domagus. Goods.
<voice_0x01000FEB><se_def>*: A mindless mirror of the same size but without magic. It can't penetrate the black aura.
